<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4176] analysis ui: javascript not properly handling URL decoding of input</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4176</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;attempting to input values containing &quot;%&quot; in the analysis UI causes errors.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example of the bug, using the solr example configs...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) load &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1/analysis&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1/analysis&lt;/a&gt; in a browser&lt;br/&gt;
2) select field type &quot;text_general&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
3) enter into either text box: {&lt;tt&gt;foo%bar&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
4) click the &quot;Analyze Values&quot; button.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;results...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Window location is updated to be: &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1/analysis?analysis.fieldvalue=foo%25bar&amp;amp;analysis.query=&amp;amp;analysis.fieldtype=text_general&amp;amp;verbose_output=1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1/analysis?analysis.fieldvalue=foo%25bar&amp;amp;analysis.query=&amp;amp;analysis.fieldtype=text_general&amp;amp;verbose_output=1&lt;/a&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Note: &quot;%&quot; has been properly encoded in URL&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;page does not display any analyis, and text areas are now empty (although text_general field type is still selected)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;web dev error console indicates...
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Error: URIError: malformed URI sequence
Source File: http://localhost:8983/solr/js/scripts/analysis.js
Line: 132
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
